                                        YouTube to MP3 Converter
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-medium text-white/80 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
                                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                                        Download Shorts Instantly
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-medium text-white/80 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
                                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
                                        Unlimited Turbo Speed
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                             </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Instagram Section -->
                    <div class="group relative bg-[#18181b] border border-white/5 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 overflow-hidden hover:border-pink-500/30 transition-colors duration-500">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-pink-600/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 group-hover:bg-pink-600/20 transition-all duration-500"></div>
                        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
                             <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-yellow-400 via-pink-500 to-purple-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_30px_-5px_rgba(236,72,153,0.5)]">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"/></svg>
                             </div>
                             <div class="space-y-6 flex-1">
                                <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white">Download <span class="text-pink-500">Instagram</span> Reels and Stories</h2>
                                <p class="text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed">
                                    Simple and no sign-up. Save <strong>Reels, Stories, IGTV</strong> and photos. Your ultimate tool for downloading Instagram content with total privacy.
                                </p>
                                <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-medium text-white/80 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
                                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pink-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                                        Download Reels No Watermark
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-medium text-white/80 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
                                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pink-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                                        Save Stories (Before they Expire)
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                             </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- TikTok Section -->
                    <div class="group relative bg-[#18181b] border border-white/5 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 overflow-hidden hover:border-cyan-500/30 transition-colors duration-500">
