                                    Download viral TikTok videos totally <strong>clean, no logos or user names</strong>. Extract just the audio for your edits or save the original HD video.
                                </p>
                                <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-medium text-white/80 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
                                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                                        Automatic Watermark Removal
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-medium text-white/80 bg-white/5 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
                                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3"></path></svg>
                                        Download TikTok Audio (MP3)
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
